#!/bin/bash
PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/bin:/opt/homebrew/bin git --no-pager diff | llm -m gpt-5.2 --no-stream "You are a strict and senior software engineer. Please review these unstaged code changes. You MUST check for the following project guideline violations: (1) Returning Entities directly from controllers instead of using DTOs. (2) Hardcoded values instead of constants. (3) Usage of deprecated methods. (4) Duplicated frontend code instead of reusing/creating shared components. (5) Usage of fully qualified names inline instead of proper imports, and presence of unused imports. (6) Usage of @Autowired field injection instead of @RequiredArgsConstructor with private final fields (unless justified), or dependencies scattered instead of being placed at the top of the class. Also identify any potential bugs, edge cases, performance optimizations, and maintainability issues. Output your review in markdown format." > .ai_review_report.md
